name: Streadata.io API Gallery - Google Task Queue
description: This is a repository of google task queue APIs, self-contained as a Github repository, with HTML and YAML representations of the APIs and their surrounding operations.

apis.name: Google Task Queue
apis.description: The Task Queue API lets applications perform work, called tasks, asynchronously outside of a user request. If an app needs to execute work in the background, it adds tasks to task queues. The tasks are executed later, by scalable App Engine worker services in your application.
